org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.couchdb.dialect.backend.json.impl

Class AssociationDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.couchdb.dialect.backend.json.impl.Document
      • org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.couchdb.dialect.backend.json.impl.AssociationDocument

  • public class AssociationDocument
extends Document
    Represents an association stored as a separate CouchDB document. Used to serialize and deserialize the JSON with the following structure: { "_id": "", "_rev": " ", "$type": "association", "rows": [{ "key": "value" }] }
    Author:
    Andrea Boriero <dreborier@gmail.com>, Gunnar Morling
